#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:7
msgid "Working with the Contents of Terminal Windows"
msgstr "Arbeta med innehållet i Terminal Windows"

#. (itstool) path: item/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:10
msgid "To scroll through previous commands and output:"
msgstr "För att bläddra bland tidigare kommandon och utdata:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:11
msgid "Perform one of the following actions:"
msgstr "Utför någon av följande åtgärder:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:16
msgid ""
"Use the scrollbar, which is usually displayed on the right of the terminal "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Använd rullningslisten, som vanligtvis visas till höger i terminalfönstret."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:20
msgid ""
"Press the <keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Page Up</key></keyseq>, "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Page Down</key></keyseq>, "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Home</key></keyseq>, or "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>End</key></keyseq> keys."
msgstr ""
"Tryck på <keyseq><key>Skift</key><key>Sida upp</key></keyseq>, "
"<keyseq><key>Skift</key><key>Sidan ner</key></keyseq>, "
"<keyseq><key>Skift</key><key>Hem</key></keyseq>eller "
"<keyseq><key>Skift</key><key>Slut</key></keyseq> knappar."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:24
msgid ""
"The number of lines that you can scroll back to in the terminal window is "
"determined by the <gui style=\"guilabel\">Scrollback</gui> setting in the "
"<gui style=\"guilabel\">Scrolling</gui> tabbed section of the <gui "
"style=\"guilabel\">Editing Profile</gui> dialog. You can also scroll up or "
"down one line at a time by pressing "
"<keyseq><key>Control</key><key>Shift</key><key>Up</key></keyseq> or "
"<keyseq><key>Control</key><key>Shift</key><key>Down</key></keyseq>."
msgstr ""
"Antalet rader som du kan bläddra tillbaka till i terminalfönstret bestäms av"
" inställningen <gui style=\"guilabel\">Scrollback</gui> i fliken <gui "
"style=\"guilabel\">Scrolling</gui> i dialogrutan <gui "
"style=\"guilabel\">Editing Profile</gui>. Du kan också bläddra upp eller ner"
" en rad i taget genom att trycka på "
"<keyseq><key>Kontroll</key><key>Skift</key><key>Upp</key></keyseq> eller "
"<keyseq><key>Kontroll</key><key>Skifta</key><key>Ner</key></keyseq>."

#. (itstool) path: item/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:28
msgid "To select and copy text:"
msgstr "Markera och kopiera text:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:29
msgid "You can select text in any of the following ways:"
msgstr "Du kan markera text på något av följande sätt:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:34
msgid ""
"To select a character at a time, click on the first character that you want "
"to select and drag the mouse to the last character that you want to select."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill markera ett tecken i taget klickar du på det första tecknet som "
"du vill markera och drar musen till det sista tecknet som du vill markera."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:38
msgid ""
"To select a word at a time, double-click on the first word that you want to "
"select and drag the mouse to the last word that you want to select. Symbols "
"are selected individually."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill markera ett ord i taget dubbelklickar du på det första ordet som "
"du vill markera och drar muspekaren till det sista ordet som du vill "
"markera. Symboler markeras individuellt."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:42
msgid ""
"To select a line at a time, triple-click on the first line that you want to "
"select and drag the mouse to the last line that you want to select."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill markera en rad i taget trippelklickar du på den första raden som "
"du vill markera och drar musen till den sista raden som du vill markera."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:46
msgid ""
"These actions select all text between the first and last items. For all text"
" selections, <app>MATE Terminal</app> copies the selected text into the "
"clipboard when you release the mouse button. To explicitly copy the selected"
" text, choose <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">Edit</gui><gui "
"style=\"guimenuitem\">Copy</gui></guiseq>."
msgstr ""
"Dessa åtgärder väljer all text mellan det första och det sista objektet. För"
" alla textmarkeringar kopierar <app>MATE Terminal</app> den markerade texten"
" till urklipp när du släpper musknappen. Om du uttryckligen vill kopiera den"
" markerade texten väljer du <guiseq><gui "
"style=\"guimenu\">Redigera</gui><gui "
"style=\"guimenuitem\">Kopiera</gui></guiseq>."

#. (itstool) path: item/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:50
msgid "To paste text into a terminal:"
msgstr "Klistra in text i en terminal:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:51
msgid ""
"If you previously copied text to the clipboard, you can paste the text into "
"a terminal by performing one of the following actions:"
msgstr ""
"Om du tidigare har kopierat text till urklipp kan du klistra in texten i en "
"terminal genom att utföra någon av följande åtgärder:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:55
msgid ""
"To paste text that you copied by selection only, middle-click at the command"
" prompt. If you do not have a middle mouse button, refer to the X Server "
"documentation for information about how to emulate the middle mouse button."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill klistra in text som du kopierade genom att endast markera den "
"klickar du med mittknappen i kommandotolken. Om du inte har en mittmusknapp "
"finns det information om hur du emulerar mittmusknappen i dokumentationen "
"för X Server."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:59
msgid ""
"To paste text that you explicitly copied, choose <guiseq><gui "
"style=\"guimenu\">Edit</gui><gui style=\"guimenuitem\">Paste</gui></guiseq>."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill klistra in text som du uttryckligen har kopierat väljer du "
"<guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">Redigera</gui><gui "
"style=\"guimenuitem\">Klistra in</gui></guiseq>."

#. (itstool) path: item/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:65
msgid "To drag a file name into a terminal window:"
msgstr "Så här drar du ett filnamn till ett terminalfönster:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:66
msgid ""
"You can drag a file name to a terminal from another application such as a "
"file manager. The terminal displays the path and the full name of the file."
msgstr ""
"Du kan dra ett filnamn till en terminal från ett annat program, t.ex. en "
"filhanterare. Terminalen visar sökvägen och det fullständiga namnet på "
"filen."

#. (itstool) path: item/title
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:70
msgid "To access a link:"
msgstr "För att komma åt en länk:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:71
msgid ""
"To access a Uniform Resource Locator (URL) that is displayed in a terminal, "
"perform the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Gör så här om du vill komma åt en URL (Uniform Resource Locator) som visas i"
" en terminal:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-contents.page:73
msgid ""
"Move the mouse over the URL until the URL is underlined. Right-click on the "
"URL to open a popup menu. Choose <gui style=\"guimenuitem\">Open Link</gui> "
"to start a link application and display the file located at the URL."
msgstr ""
"För musen över URL-adressen tills den är understruken. Högerklicka på URL-"
"adressen för att öppna en popup-meny. Välj <gui style=\"guimenuitem\">Open "
"Link</gui> för att starta ett länkprogram och visa filen som finns på "
"URL:en."

#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: C/mate-terminal-encoding.page:7
msgid "To Change the Character Encoding"
msgstr "Så här ändrar du teckenkodningen"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/mate-terminal-encoding.page:8
msgid ""
"To change the list of character encodings displayed in the <gui "
"style=\"guisubmenu\">Set Character Encoding</gui> menu, perform the "
"following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Gör så här om du vill ändra listan över teckenkodningar som visas i menyn "
"<gui style=\"guisubmenu\">Set Character Encoding (Ange teckenkodning</gui> "
"):"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/mate-terminal-encoding.page:11
msgid ""
"Choose <guiseq><gui style=\"guimenu\">Terminal</gui><gui "
"style=\"guisubmenu\">Set Character Encoding</gui><gui "
"style=\"guimenuitem\">Add or Remove</gui></guiseq>. To add an encoding to "
"the <gui style=\"guisubmenu\">Set Character Encoding</gui> menu, select the "
"encoding in the <gui style=\"guilabel\">Available encodings</gui> list box, "
