#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/mate-terminal-introduction.page:18
msgid ""
"<app>MATE Terminal</app> emulates the <app>xterm</app> application developed"
" by the X Consortium. In turn, the <app>xterm</app> application emulates the"
" DEC VT102 terminal and also supports the DEC VT220 escape sequences. An "
"escape sequence is a series of characters that starts with the "
"<key>Esc</key> character. <app>MATE Terminal</app> accepts all of the escape"
" sequences that the VT102 and VT220 terminals use for functions such as to "
"position the cursor and to clear the screen."
msgstr ""
"<app>MATE Terminal</app> emulerar <app>xterm-applikationen</app> som "
"utvecklats av X Consortium. Programmet <app>xterm</app> emulerar i sin tur "
"DEC VT102-terminalen och stöder även DEC VT220 escape-sekvenser. En escape-"
"sekvens är en serie tecken som börjar med <key>Esc-tecknet</key>. <app>MATE "
"Terminal</app> accepterar alla de escape-sekvenser som VT102- och "
"VT220-terminalerna använder för funktioner som att positionera markören och "
"rensa skärmen."

